        <briefdescription>
<para>Channel Transmission Endpoint. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This is an image of the remote&apos;s rx.</para>
<para>The MTU and MPS is controlled by the remote by L2CAP_LE_CREDIT_BASED_CONNECTION_REQ/RSP or L2CAP_CONFIGURATION_REQ. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
